                              Размеры полей: правое 0,9.
                           </seg>
                           <seg xml:lang="en"><rs type="execution" ref="execution.xml#scalpro"/> On the front. Broken off on all sides except the right; badly weathered and damaged by tidal action in sea water. Margins: right 0,9.</seg>
